---
// index.astro
import "./index.css"
---
<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>lev's site</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="box">
			<div class="top">
				<p> MAIN </p>
			</div>
			<div class="bottom">
				<div class="bottom-left">
					<div class="introblock active" data-target="main">main</div>
					<div class="introblock" data-target="blog">blog</div>
					<div class="introblock" data-target="navi">navi</div>
				</div>
				<div class="bottom-right">
					<div class="intro-content active" id="main">
						<h1> MAIN 页简介 </h1>
						<p> MAIN 页提供了对其他页的索引。</p>
						<p> 点击左侧选项卡，可以查看对应页面的简介及内容概览。 </p>
					</div>
					<div class="intro-content" id="blog">
						<h2>Blog</h2>
						<p>这里是博客介绍</p>
						<ul>
							<li>技术</li>
							<li>随笔</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="intro-content" id="navi">
						<h2>Navigation</h2>
						<p>这里是导航页</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	<script type="module" src="/src/scripts/intro.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>